&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4&quot;&gt;We are currently looking for an Associate Sales Representative (ASR) to join our Women&#39;s Health sales team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;5&quot;&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated and ambitious sales professional with 1-3 years of experience (ideally in medical sales). This person is driven, competitive, and resourceful, with a strong desire to learn and grow in a fast-paced, performance-oriented environment. This person demonstrates strong business aptitude, takes initiative, and is comfortable working both independently and as part of a high-performing team.&lt;/p&gt;
