&lt;p&gt;Serves as a model for standards and behavior performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Participate in the drafting of SOW and processing of select research samples through the CLIA lab. Leads, directs and manages high performance teams with accountability for operations, quality, customer service, and success of assigned departments and product lines.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identifies and champions development of departmental key performance indicators (KPI) and analyze for opportunities to optimize department performance.&lt;/p&gt;
