&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Identifies and champions development of departmental key performance indicators (KPI) and analyze for opportunities to optimize department performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Directs Production Laboratory personal in support of activities for manufacturing that will include method validation, method transfer, and in-process testing.&lt;/p&gt;
